Employee CSV RAG Chatbot - README

A Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) based chatbot that allows querying an Employee dataset (CSV/DB).
You can ask natural language questions like:

- "Give me all details of Paula Small"
- "What is the EmpID and DOB of Latia Costa and Paula Small?"
- "Show the department of Milton Wall"

The system retrieves relevant rows from the employee dataset, extracts structured details, and presents them in clean tabular format.

---

## 🚀 Features
- Query employees by name or employee ID  
- Retrieve single or multiple employees at once  
- Supports "all details" queries or specific fields like DOB, Department, EmpID etc.  
- Outputs answers in markdown tables for easy readability  
- Built on RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) workflow  

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- Python 3.10+
- ChromaDB → vector storage  
- Sentence Transformers / Embedding model → semantic search  
- LangChain (or custom RAG pipeline) → query processing  
- Tabulate / Markdown formatting → clean tables  
- LLM (Ollama / OpenAI / HuggingFace) → answer generation  

---

## 📂 Project Structure
employee-rag-chatbot/
│── data/                     # Employee CSV / DB files
│── main.py                   # Entry point for chatbot
│── rag_query.py              # RAG pipeline functions
│── utils.py                  # Helper functions (table formatter, column extraction etc.)
│── parse_question.py          # Logic for parsing user queries
│── requirements.txt           # Python dependencies
│── README.md                  # Project documentation
│── .gitignore                 # Ignore venv, cache, db

---

## 🔧 Installation
Clone this repository and install dependencies:
git clone https://github.com/YOUR-USERNAME/employee-rag-chatbot.git
cd employee-rag-chatbot
pip install -r requirements.txt

---

## ▶️ Usage
Run the chatbot:
python main.py

Example Queries:
- all details of Paula Small
- dob, empid of Latia Costa and Paula Small
- department of Milton Wall

Expected Output (formatted table):
## Employee Paula Small
| Column        | Value       |
|---------------|-------------|
| EmpID         | 3428        |
| Date of Birth | 30-08-1965  |
| Gender        | Female      |
| Race          | White       |

